node.text:
I know times have been tough for a lot of us, but whatever you’re going through, please know that you don’t have to do it alone. Make your mental health a top priority this year! I know I will be. Too many people are suffering and don’t know who to turn to or how to start. What I love about BetterHelp is that you can get a therapy session from the privacy of your own home. 
Check out the link in my bio for a 20% discount for the first month!! Love you guys & wishing you all nothing but happiness, peace of mind and good health always. 🙏🏼🤍 Xo Vic

node.title: I’m SO excited to be partnering with @betterhelp!

node.text:
Hi guys :) In case you didn’t know, this cool cat (@spencermusic) & I wrote & sing the final song for our movie #AfterlifeOfTheParty ! Along w/ the talented @keatonstromberg who produced. Swipe for some pics from the day we created “Home”. ♥️
It’s a fun little duet & we’re very proud of it. I think it captures the essence of the film really well & has a fun uplifting vibe. Check it out, I’ll link in stories (you can also stream everywhere) & let me know what you think! 💋🎶 Oh and keep streaming Afterlife on Netflix !! 💕BIG LOVE! Thank you thank you 🙏🏼

node.text:
In case you haven’t heard, “Afterlife of the Party” is out now on @Netflix!!! I loved making this film so much and I’m so excited it’s finally out for you guys to see! ☺️ I heard it’s the #1 movie in the US, Brazil, Mexico, Poland... WOW!!! Guys!! Beyond grateful 🥺🥺🙏🏼 
I hope it puts a smile on your face just like you guys are doing for me now! Thank you!! Go stream if you haven’t yet and let me know what you think! 💖

A few more Afterlife stills ✨ 
Guys, the movie is going to be out in LESS THAN A WEEK!! AKA this coming Thursday! 😱 I’m so excited for you all to see this film. Making it was such an unforgettable experience with some of the most kind & talented people I’ve ever had the pleasure of working with. I hope you guys like it 🤍. Only on @netflix ! See you there 💋 #AfterlifeOfTheParty #Sept2
